@startuml
title Desktop - trajectory conversion path (OSM to SUMO to CSV steps)

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam maxMessageSize 220

actor "Operator" as Op
participant "DatasetConversionPage" as DCP
participant "DownloadWorker" as DW
collections "Overpass API\n(OSM XML)" as OSM
collections "netconvert\n(SUMO)" as NC
participant "NetworkLoaderWorker" as NLW
participant "NetworkParser" as NP
participant "SimulationView" as SV
participant "RouteLoadWorker\n(optional)" as RLW
participant "StepGenerationWorker" as SGW
collections "run_csv_to_steps\n/ utils" as RCS

== Map extent and OSM to SUMO ==
Op -> DCP : set bounding box\n(south, west, north, east),\n map basename, output folder
Op -> DCP : download / build map
DCP -> DW : start (bbox, paths)
DW -> OSM : Overpass query for bbox
OSM --> DW : .osm file
DW -> NC : netconvert + typemap\n- to .net.xml, .rou.xml, .sumocfg
NC --> DW : SUMO network on disk
DW --> DCP : success

DCP -> NLW : load generated .net.xml
NLW -> NP : parse geometry
NLW --> DCP : NetworkParser
DCP -> SV : load_network(parser)
SV --> Op : map in scene

== Trajectory CSVs ==
Op -> DCP : select main (and optional) CSVs,\n validation / path checks

== Optional: inspect route matching ==
Op -> DCP : choose route index, **Show route**
DCP -> RLW : load trip polyline
RLW --> DCP : GPS polyline, invalid segments,\n trim hints
DCP -> SV : draw polyline, green/orange\ncandidate edges, diagnostics
Op -> DCP : (optional) adjust checkboxes\n(fix segments, trim, …)

== Dataset generation parameters ==
Op -> DCP : set output dir, trajectory range\n(start--last), sampling period,\n parallel workers, compress, sorted CSV, …

== Generate dataset (steps) ==
Op -> DCP : **Start** (step conversion)
DCP -> SGW : start worker
SGW -> RCS : run_csv_to_steps(\n  csv, network, output, …)
RCS --> SGW : step files, trajectories
SGW --> DCP : progress / finished
DCP --> Op : log + progress UI

@enduml
